### Agent Router — Database（规则路由）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/workflows/agent-route
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "orders表按user_id查询为什么慢？"
}

### Agent Router — RAG（规则路由）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/workflows/agent-route
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "退款政策是什么？",
  "topK": 5
}

### Agent Router — Chat（LLM / fallback 路由）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/workflows/agent-route
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "你好，今天天气怎么样？",
  "sessionId": "demo"
}
